# Deny by default: a remote builder receives only the audited application
# inputs, never local ops, campaign material, editor state or private env files.
**

!Dockerfile
!.dockerignore
!.npmrc.security
!package.json
!package-lock.json
!tsconfig.json
!requirements-whisper.txt
!native/
!native/no-dump-exec.c
!native/no-dump-preload.c

!src/
!src/**
!docs/
!docs/**
!scripts/
!scripts/transcribe-local.py
